1:1: COMMENT NOTE
1:7: STR_LIT "
    斯篇專試「明斷」之機巧。
    借賈島《尋隱者不遇》之尋訪層次，
    以驗「若」、「或若」、「若非」之連鎖，
    並辨「雲」、「霧」迷障之理，
    以觀編譯器決斷吉凶、尋芳探幽之趣也。
"
9:1: HERE_ARE i have
9:8: NUMBER_LIT 1
9:10: VAR_TYPE str
9:15: SAID called
9:22: STR_LIT "松下問童子，欲尋隱者蹤。"
9:40: PRINT print
11:1: HERE_IS_A has a
11:7: VAR_TYPE num
11:11: NUMBER_LIT 3
11:14: NAME_IT name it
11:22: IDENT '尋訪線索'
13:1: COMMENT NOTE
13:7: STR_LIT " 驗證 若 與 若非 之嵌套 "
14:1: IF if
14:4: IDENT '尋訪線索'
14:11: EXP_LOGIC >
14:13: NUMBER_LIT 2
14:15: TOPIC topic
15:5: HERE_IS_A has a
15:11: VAR_TYPE str
15:15: STR_LIT "想當然耳！線索俱全，必能尋得隱者。"
15:37: PRINT print
16:1: ELSE else
17:5: HERE_IS_A has a
17:11: VAR_TYPE str
17:15: STR_LIT "怪哉！深山逢童子，竟問不出隻言片語？"
17:38: PRINT print
18:1: END end
20:1: COMMENT NOTE
