21:14: NUMBER_LIT 1
21:16: TOPIC topic
22:5: HERE_IS_A has a
22:11: VAR_TYPE str
22:15: STR_LIT "童子答曰：『言師採藥去。』"
22:33: PRINT print
23:1: ELSE_IF else if
23:9: IDENT '尋訪線索'
23:16: EXP_LOGIC ==
23:19: NUMBER_LIT 2
23:21: TOPIC topic
24:5: HERE_IS_A has a
24:11: VAR_TYPE str
24:15: STR_LIT "童子指山曰：『只在此山中。』"
24:34: PRINT print
25:1: ELSE_IF else if
25:9: IDENT '尋訪線索'
25:16: EXP_LOGIC ==
25:19: NUMBER_LIT 3
25:21: TOPIC topic
26:5: HERE_IS_A has a
26:11: VAR_TYPE str
26:15: STR_LIT "童子搖頭曰：『雲深不知處。』"
26:34: PRINT print
27:1: ELSE else
28:5: HERE_IS_A has a
28:11: VAR_TYPE str
28:15: STR_LIT "奇了，童子竟言他物！"
28:30: PRINT print
29:1: END end
